{"tid":1950672,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"確診女警光復香港？ - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-03-30T12:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T13:39:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db1d9c2c1ced5f999b7593e9d61f33a37a2a10a2","tid":1950672,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200330/20889897/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200330%2F20889897%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2U2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=b4178b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200330%2F20889897%2F&h=1dd37059\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200330/20889897/</a><br />\n<br />\n確診女警光復香港？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200330/large/1585464988_273e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585464988_273e.jpg&h=1927f117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷史證明，敗亡攬炒要靠女人。褒姒、妲己、呂后、武則天、江青、慈禧、林鄭毒娥&hellip;&hellip;22歲鄭姓女警是新秀。<br />\n<br />\n這回不待港人稱呼，警隊也會目之為「黑警」。該名隸屬深水埗警區軍裝巡邏小隊的女警已確診武漢肺炎，一人中招旁人岌岌可危，生活多姿多彩多朋友：到尖沙咀曾有染疫者去過的All Night Long酒吧消遣，與30名警員到新界南室內練靶場練槍、練槍後3同袍去「飲嘢」、繼續當值&hellip;&hellip;且被爆在確診前抽血、做靜脈注射及做心電圖時，死不肯戴口罩，在房內咳嗽播毒，勸喻無效，結果禍及2名醫護人員一不適一要隔離檢疫──難道黑警受包庇，有特權，可不為大眾利益及衞生着想？如此囂張、無良、自私，禍害多少人？俗謂「生累街坊死累朋友」，也許不止，所有無辜者多得佢唔少。毒娥快出來表演哽咽：「對唔對得住喺逆境中抗疫嘅醫護？」令PK鄧蒙羞？未必，上樑不正下樑歪，日夜身教言教，才出來此等質素之物體。<br />\n<br />\n也很奇怪，香港因毒娥不肯在重要時刻封關堵截毒源，現社區傳播疫情日趨嚴重，警隊也屬高危，何以「只得」3人確診？怕影響軍心士氣，管治威信？不經無能政府公告，「自成軍國」去處理？這個人物關係鏈密封不漏了？光復香港也靠它？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"7f7b5550f3de817a0ff8198fe542478e19bdf282","tid":1950672,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:51:03.000Z","msg":"黑警肺部發光<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovFm5dh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovFm5dh.jpg&h=5da3c7ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b380d89783a7de991ded5312e19ff44ad72c301","tid":1950672,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"請你將呢份愛&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"482058fa38033133344ce78698761f02b3f3e1c1","tid":1950672,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857159aef77424caaf6d2e06db4e5244fe66efc0","tid":1950672,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"家陣瘋狂落閘放狗<del>散毒</del><br />\n擺明想光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d9e4daf5b08c014812213ac1da2f06f078418a","tid":1950672,"uid":251614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:08:17.000Z","msg":"呢個係唔係寫胭脂扣果個李碧華？"},{"pid":"1b0124cf0d624f1d2b121fbdea9e34882dfe01ce","tid":1950672,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">現社區傳播疫情日趨嚴重，警隊也屬高危，何以「只得」3人確診？怕影響軍心士氣，管治威信？不經無能政府公告，「自成軍國」去處理？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3179babb99205d7f2ec2d6b43739ea56deea568a","tid":1950672,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"靜靜雞<br />\n武肺好小氣"},{"pid":"988ce233e591c4bf31fa71109dba2e33ab3a5932","tid":1950672,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57d9e4daf5b08c014812213ac1da2f06f078418a","tid":1950672,